@node InUsEd_TabConfAccess "Internal User Editor: Conference Acess Edit"

Command: @{b}Conference Acess Edit@{ub}

The Tab key invokes a small conference access editor which looks like this:

                     @{b}-+ User Conference Access Editor +-

XS Num. Conference Name                XS Num. Conference Name
------------------------------------------------------------------------------@{ub}
@{fg shine}*@{fg text} [  @{fg fill}1@{fg text}] Basement                       @{fg shine}*@{fg text} [  @{fg fill}2@{fg text}] First Floor
@{fg shine}*@{fg text} [  @{fg fill}3@{fg text}] Household and Toys               [  @{fg fill}4@{fg text}]
  [  @{fg fill}5@{fg text}]                                  [  @{fg fill}6@{fg text}]
  [  @{fg fill}7@{fg text}]                                  [  @{fg fill}8@{fg text}]
  [  @{fg fill}9@{fg text}]                                  [ @{fg fill}10@{fg text}]
  [ @{fg fill}11@{fg text}]                                  [ @{fg fill}12@{fg text}]
  [ @{fg fill}13@{fg text}]                                  [ @{fg fill}14@{fg text}]
  [ @{fg fill}15@{fg text}]                                  [ @{fg fill}16@{fg text}]
  [ @{fg fill}17@{fg text}]                                  [ @{fg fill}18@{fg text}]
  [ @{fg fill}19@{fg text}]                                  [ @{fg fill}20@{fg text}]

(@{fg fill}S@{fg text})ave (@{fg fill}A@{fg text})bort (@{fg fill}N@{fg text})ext Page (@{fg fill}P@{fg text})rev Page Status:
Enter (@{bg fill}C@{bg back})onference Number(s) to Toggle: @{fg fill}>@{fg text}:

-where you may rock around with the cursor keys and select the element under
the cursor using the Return/Enter key. An asterisk (@{fg shine}*@{fg text}) at the left side
signals that the user has access to the according conference.

Beyond that, the following additional hotkeys are available:

S - save all changes
A - abort the Conference Access Editor
N - display the next page (if you have more than 20 Conferences).
P - go back to the previous page
C - manually enter a Conference number.

@endnode

